HEADWORD: functionalism
<hw>functionalism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a psychology based
on the assumption that all mental process are useful to an organism in
adapting to the environment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>any doctrine that stresses utility or
purpose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>functionalist</ent>⟦br⟧
